### Delivery Admin - Barcode Scanning API Tests
### This file demonstrates the delivery admin barcode scanning functionality

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Login as delivery admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "delivery@demo.com",
  "password": "delivery123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("delivery_token", response.body.token);
%}

### 2. Get delivery statistics for today
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{delivery_token}}

### 3. Get all pending deliveries for today
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery/pending-deliveries
Authorization: Bearer {{delivery_token}}

### 4. Scan user barcode to get their pending items
### Replace with actual credential number from user profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery/scan-user
Authorization: Bearer {{delivery_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "barcode": "123456789"
}

### 5. Mark item as delivered by scanning
### Replace userBarcode and orderItemId with actual values from previous response
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery/scan-item
Authorization: Bearer {{delivery_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userBarcode": "123456789",
  "orderItemId": 1
}

### 6. Scan user barcode again to verify remaining items
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery/scan-user
Authorization: Bearer {{delivery_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "barcode": "123456789"
}

### 7. Check updated statistics after delivery
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{delivery_token}}

### Test Error Cases

### 8. Try to scan non-existent user barcode
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery/scan-user
Authorization: Bearer {{delivery_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "barcode": "999999999"
}

### 9. Try to deliver item with wrong user barcode
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery/scan-item
Authorization: Bearer {{delivery_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userBarcode": "000000000",
  "orderItemId": 1
}

### 10. Try to deliver item that's not in IN_DELIVERY status
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery/scan-item
Authorization: Bearer {{delivery_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userBarcode": "123456789",
  "orderItemId": 999
}

### 11. Login as regular admin to prepare items for delivery (set to IN_DELIVERY status)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@demo.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.token);
%}

### 12. Bulk update items to IN_DELIVERY status for testing
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/bulk-status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deliveryDate": "2024-12-15T00:00:00Z",
  "status": "IN_DELIVERY",
  "previousStatus": "IN_PROGRESS"
}
